WEBVTT

00:23.800 --> 00:25.600
This is actually really good.

00:25.680 --> 00:27.040
Minister Wu has arrived.

00:27.560 --> 00:28.680
HALL OF THE SUPREME ULTIMATE

00:28.760 --> 00:29.960
Minister Wu has arrived.

00:30.040 --> 00:31.160
-Minister.
-Minister.

00:31.240 --> 00:32.520
Minister Fang has arrived.

00:48.880 --> 00:50.720
Earlier in the throne hall,

00:50.800 --> 00:52.640
I only caught a glimpse of you, General.

00:52.720 --> 00:55.840
I have the utmost admiration
for how you slew the rebel

00:55.920 --> 00:57.240
Prince Changxin.

00:57.320 --> 01:00.520
What an honor tonight.
Allow me to offer you a toast first.

01:03.800 --> 01:04.640
Please.

01:07.920 --> 01:08.760
The General has quite a capacity!

01:08.840 --> 01:10.320
-Indeed.
-Indeed.

01:10.920 --> 01:12.600
General Fan, young and accomplished,

01:12.680 --> 01:13.520
renowned far and wide,

01:13.600 --> 01:14.680
with the bearing of a true hero.

01:15.760 --> 01:17.160
To slay Prince Changxin,

01:17.240 --> 01:18.560
truly remarkable.

01:18.640 --> 01:20.920
-Indeed.
-Allow me to offer you a toast.

01:24.920 --> 01:26.160
If she keeps drinking like this,

01:26.240 --> 01:28.840
that pig-slaughtering woman
will surely make a fool of herself.

01:30.200 --> 01:31.160
Forget her.

01:32.720 --> 01:34.720
Why hasn't the young master arrived yet?

01:35.440 --> 01:37.440
LET IT BE

01:37.520 --> 01:38.520
Another toast to General Fan.

01:38.600 --> 01:41.200
Grand Tutor, I hear your heart condition
has flared up recently.

01:41.280 --> 01:43.080
-Has it improved at all?
-Much better.

01:43.160 --> 01:44.360
I've been deeply concerned.

01:44.440 --> 01:45.640
Quite the capacity.

01:45.720 --> 01:47.360
That pig-slaughtering woman
throws her weight around.

01:47.440 --> 01:49.600
-We're all at our wit's end.
-Indeed.

01:52.680 --> 01:54.000
Enough watching. Come.

01:54.080 --> 01:55.760
Let me share a few drinks with all of you.

01:55.840 --> 01:56.880
Good things come in pairs.

01:56.960 --> 01:58.040
We must enjoy ourselves
to the fullest tonight.

01:58.120 --> 01:59.440
Allow me to offer you
another toast, General.

01:59.520 --> 02:00.360
Come.

02:13.880 --> 02:16.520
Isn't tonight's banquet granted
by His Majesty in my honor?

02:17.480 --> 02:18.880
You are all under
Chancellor Wei's patronage.

02:19.760 --> 02:23.120
Why do you keep toasting
only the Flower-Adorned General?

02:23.200 --> 02:24.440
Could it be

02:24.520 --> 02:25.960
you look down on me?

02:28.320 --> 02:29.440
The Marquis jests.

02:29.520 --> 02:30.960
General Fan arrived first,

02:31.040 --> 02:33.040
so we thought to warm things up a bit.

02:33.680 --> 02:36.360
Allow me to toast on your return.

02:44.440 --> 02:45.320
Marquis,

02:45.400 --> 02:47.120
we serve the same court.

02:47.640 --> 02:49.200
Was this necessary?

02:49.800 --> 02:51.040
Minister Fang, right?

02:51.880 --> 02:53.480
As Vice Minister of Revenue,

02:54.000 --> 02:55.880
you're responsible
for grain shipments to the border?

02:56.480 --> 02:57.680
And if I am?

02:57.760 --> 03:00.200
You nearly sparked a revolt in Jizhou
with your incompetence.

03:00.280 --> 03:02.000
I haven't even called you to account yet,

03:02.520 --> 03:03.520
and you have the nerve
to act like a proper official?

03:03.600 --> 03:04.560
You--

03:05.520 --> 03:07.800
Today is meant to celebrate the Marquis.

03:07.880 --> 03:09.240
Let's not discuss official matters.

03:09.320 --> 03:10.920
Minister Fang, you've spilled wine
all over yourself.

03:11.000 --> 03:12.440
Go rest a while.

03:13.040 --> 03:14.320
Marquis, please.

03:15.360 --> 03:17.240
The Chancellor will arrive shortly.

03:19.000 --> 03:20.640
-Let's go.
-Marquis, I take my leave.

03:20.720 --> 03:22.120
This is utterly outrageous.

03:23.640 --> 03:25.200
Grand Tutor, come, fill your cup.

03:25.280 --> 03:27.920
The real show is just beginning.

03:28.440 --> 03:31.080
We shall sit tight
and watch it unfold slowly.

03:32.600 --> 03:34.400
I was half afraid you'd come to blows.

03:35.280 --> 03:37.400
You give these parasites too much credit.

03:38.080 --> 03:40.600
Every one of them is rotten inside,

03:40.680 --> 03:42.320
and they all feel inferior to me.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.680
They wouldn't dare start anything bold.

03:46.640 --> 03:49.080
Don't worry. I'll leave early,

03:49.160 --> 03:50.760
and Gongsun will handle things from there.

03:54.520 --> 03:55.360
Sit.

03:58.040 --> 04:01.520
His Majesty has arrived!

04:01.600 --> 04:03.680
We welcome Your Majesty.

04:04.600 --> 04:05.960
We welcome Your Majesty.

04:06.480 --> 04:08.040
Grand Tutor, you've recovered.

04:08.120 --> 04:09.000
Excellent.

04:10.040 --> 04:11.280
I'm unworthy

04:11.880 --> 04:13.480
of Your Majesty's concern.

04:14.000 --> 04:16.600
These past days,
Chancellor Wei has worked hard.

04:17.760 --> 04:20.560
I'm always like this.
I don't find it hard work.

04:20.640 --> 04:23.080
But Grand Tutor,
you should take care of yourself.

04:23.160 --> 04:25.120
Rest when you need to.

04:27.200 --> 04:28.240
Thank you.

04:29.720 --> 04:31.960
Both of you are pillars of the state.

04:32.040 --> 04:34.440
Today brings double happiness.

04:34.520 --> 04:35.520
My heart is truly pleased.

04:37.560 --> 04:39.840
In quelling the Chongzhou rebellion,

04:39.920 --> 04:41.520
the Marquis of Wu'an faced deadly odds

04:41.600 --> 04:42.920
and rendered the greatest service.

04:43.480 --> 04:46.280
The four northwestern prefectures
have remained secure

04:46.360 --> 04:47.920
thanks to his guardianship.

04:48.440 --> 04:51.640
I specially bestow upon the Marquis
of Wu'an the Dragon Spring Sword,

04:51.720 --> 04:54.320
forged by our founding emperor himself.

04:54.400 --> 04:55.920
From above, it can slay a foolish ruler.

05:01.160 --> 05:02.520
From below, execute treacherous ministers.

05:02.600 --> 05:03.760
This expresses my heart.

05:05.880 --> 05:06.800
Present it.

05:13.000 --> 05:14.600
The Dragon Spring Sword…

05:17.480 --> 05:19.360
truly lives up to its name.

05:23.960 --> 05:25.840
It can slay a foolish ruler from above

05:28.320 --> 05:30.120
and execute treacherous ministers.

05:37.440 --> 05:38.320
A fine blade indeed.

05:40.760 --> 05:42.480
But my heart is with the realm.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.720
I am devoted to my duties.

05:44.240 --> 05:46.120
The Dragon Spring Sword is too precious.

05:46.640 --> 05:48.960
No one but Your Majesty is worthy of it.

05:54.720 --> 05:56.320
I am well aware

05:56.400 --> 05:57.920
of the Marquis of Wu'an's loyalty.

05:59.000 --> 06:00.240
Tonight's palace banquet,

06:00.960 --> 06:02.920
let no minister leave sober.

06:03.000 --> 06:04.720
Thank you, Your Majesty.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.320
I'll go change first.

06:07.640 --> 06:09.280
His Majesty withdraws for a moment.

06:10.720 --> 06:12.640
We respectfully see His Majesty off.

06:14.360 --> 06:15.240
Your Majesty.

06:16.400 --> 06:17.240
Your Majesty.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.480
Grand Princess,

06:19.560 --> 06:22.240
Empress Dowager An has sent me especially

06:22.320 --> 06:23.920
to remind you,

06:24.440 --> 06:26.280
the palace banquet is about to begin.

06:26.880 --> 06:28.520
Please don't be late.

06:35.080 --> 06:37.200
Forgive me, Your Highness.
I didn't mean to.

06:38.760 --> 06:41.200
-You… You wretched maid. How dare you--
-It's nothing.

06:43.960 --> 06:46.320
Today's banquet
honors the Marquis of Wu'an.

06:46.400 --> 06:47.240
Not the time for anger.

06:47.880 --> 06:49.280
-You…
-You may go now.

06:49.360 --> 06:50.320
Yes.

06:50.840 --> 06:51.880
You…

06:53.720 --> 06:58.280
I failed to discipline her properly.
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.280
I must go change.

07:00.360 --> 07:03.640
I'm sure neither the Marquis of Wu'an
nor my brother will mind.

07:04.280 --> 07:06.120
This…

07:07.200 --> 07:08.280
Your Highness.

07:11.640 --> 07:14.080
His Majesty is waiting for you.

07:15.600 --> 07:16.920
Xie Zheng, Wei Yan,

07:17.000 --> 07:18.040
uncle and nephew, both the same.

07:18.120 --> 07:19.520
Neither ever saw me as worth their notice.

07:19.600 --> 07:20.640
They deserve to die.

07:21.520 --> 07:22.840
Both of them.

07:24.560 --> 07:25.960
If that's how it is,

07:26.040 --> 07:27.800
don't blame me
for not giving you a chance.

09:14.560 --> 09:19.040
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

09:21.800 --> 09:25.240
HALL OF THE SUPREME ULTIMATE

09:35.840 --> 09:38.200
Ministers, this atmosphere is all wrong.

09:38.280 --> 09:40.000
Keep the music playing, keep dancing.

09:40.080 --> 09:41.120
Drink up!

09:41.200 --> 09:42.760
-After you.
-Please.

09:44.760 --> 09:45.920
-Quite nice, isn't it?
-Yes.

09:47.720 --> 09:48.560
-Grand Tutor.
-Your Majesty.

09:48.640 --> 09:50.200
Doesn't Dayin still depend on me?

09:50.800 --> 09:51.920
Of course.

09:52.000 --> 09:53.880
Dayin's prosperity for generations

09:53.960 --> 09:56.720
to come rests entirely
on Your Majesty's wise and solitary rule.

09:56.800 --> 09:58.720
What would the realm do without me?

09:58.800 --> 09:59.720
Right?

09:59.800 --> 10:00.640
So true.

10:02.960 --> 10:05.040
A drunk's a drunk, noble or common.

10:05.640 --> 10:06.760
An emperor with too much wine,

10:06.840 --> 10:08.320
boasting away,

10:08.840 --> 10:10.160
looks just like Uncle Zhao.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.520
Chancellor Wei.

10:17.120 --> 10:17.960
Gong--

10:20.840 --> 10:21.840
We've found her.

10:22.360 --> 10:24.040
The Grand Princess
has already brought her out.

10:24.120 --> 10:25.120
She's settled in Qingyuan Palace.

10:26.520 --> 10:27.800
Got to say,

10:27.880 --> 10:30.280
this outfit really suits you.

10:31.880 --> 10:33.640
-Come.
-Drink up.

10:33.720 --> 10:34.680
Thank you, Marquis.

10:36.640 --> 10:37.720
Little eunuch,

10:38.480 --> 10:40.600
bring that plate of pastries over here.

10:44.000 --> 10:45.200
Yes.

10:49.480 --> 10:51.360
Ministers, drink to your heart's content.

10:55.760 --> 10:56.800
You…

11:01.560 --> 11:02.680
Forgive me, Marquis.

11:02.760 --> 11:03.720
Forgive me, Marquis.

11:09.360 --> 11:10.240
Are you alright?

11:11.160 --> 11:12.000
It's nothing.

11:12.080 --> 11:13.840
You worthless servant.

11:13.920 --> 11:15.720
How dare you offend my Marquis of Wu'an?

11:15.800 --> 11:17.560
Guards. Take him away and punish him.

11:17.640 --> 11:18.480
Yes, Your Majesty.

11:19.120 --> 11:19.960
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

11:21.320 --> 11:22.440
At a palace banquet,

11:22.520 --> 11:23.880
it's best not to draw blood.

11:24.400 --> 11:25.760
I wouldn't want to spoil your enjoyment.

11:27.720 --> 11:29.400
The Marquis of Wu'an is truly magnanimous.

11:30.120 --> 11:31.160
You may go.

11:31.720 --> 11:32.560
There.

11:33.160 --> 11:35.000
The Marquis has pleaded for you,
you worthless servant.

11:35.080 --> 11:36.040
Now, quickly express your gratitude.

11:37.120 --> 11:37.960
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:38.040 --> 11:39.120
Thank you, Marquis of Wu'an.

11:39.200 --> 11:40.320
What are you standing there for?

11:40.880 --> 11:42.280
Escort the Marquis to change his clothes.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.560
Yes, Your Majesty.

11:47.160 --> 11:48.120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:53.720 --> 11:56.760
‎LET IT BE

12:03.920 --> 12:05.440
The emperor

12:05.960 --> 12:07.960
-Drink.
-seems a bit agitated today.

12:13.280 --> 12:14.160
Cheers.

12:30.280 --> 12:31.560
Chancellor, please stay.

12:34.080 --> 12:35.720
I hear that in the Battle of Lucheng,

12:36.320 --> 12:38.960
thanks to your timely grain shipments

12:39.600 --> 12:41.040
and your strategic…

12:41.920 --> 12:42.760
your brilliant strategy….

12:44.080 --> 12:45.280
I offer you a toast.

12:47.360 --> 12:49.000
On behalf

12:49.560 --> 12:50.800
of the border troops who fell

12:51.520 --> 12:52.840
and the border folk who died unjustly.

13:00.280 --> 13:01.280
Fan Changyu,

13:01.360 --> 13:03.000
is this a toast or an insult?

13:03.520 --> 13:04.400
Go on.

13:05.000 --> 13:06.320
A toast, of course.

13:06.840 --> 13:09.360
If not for our Chancellor's intervention,

13:09.440 --> 13:10.520
Lucheng

13:10.600 --> 13:11.440
‎RULE BY RIGHT, REIGN IN PEACE

13:11.520 --> 13:15.040
might have become another Jinzhou.

13:15.680 --> 13:17.000
No troops to call,

13:17.520 --> 13:19.080
no grain in sight.

13:19.720 --> 13:21.120
Then, it wouldn't just

13:21.640 --> 13:23.320
be General He who fell.

13:23.400 --> 13:26.840
The Marquis of Wu'an
might have died like his father,

13:28.560 --> 13:30.440
on the city wall,

13:31.200 --> 13:33.520
cut open by the enemy.

13:33.600 --> 13:35.360
And a pig-slaughtering woman like me?

13:35.440 --> 13:38.720
My fate would be nothing compared

13:39.400 --> 13:41.840
to that great traitor Wei Qilin's.

13:42.440 --> 13:43.680
So,

13:44.200 --> 13:45.520
shouldn't I offer this toast?

13:47.760 --> 13:49.440
I serve

13:49.520 --> 13:50.920
with a clear conscience.

13:55.080 --> 13:56.600
But General Fan,

13:57.760 --> 14:00.000
you truly are no match for Wei Qilin.

14:22.600 --> 14:24.160
-Chancellor.
-Where is the Marquis of Wu'an?

14:24.240 --> 14:25.880
The Marquis said
he needed to clear his head.

14:25.960 --> 14:27.040
He went toward the imperial garden.

14:28.400 --> 14:30.400
Find him immediately. Report back to me.

14:31.160 --> 14:32.000
Yes, Chancellor.

14:32.640 --> 14:33.800
Minister Fan.

14:37.240 --> 14:38.240
I toast you as well.

14:41.640 --> 14:44.000
And all of you ministers,
you've worked hard.

14:45.000 --> 14:46.440
Since I ascended the throne,

14:46.520 --> 14:48.640
I've been fortunate that civil and
military officials have worked in harmony,

14:48.720 --> 14:49.800
supporting the realm.

14:49.880 --> 14:52.680
Only thus has Dayin
enjoyed the peace it has today.

14:52.760 --> 14:55.200
I haven't failed my ancestors' legacy.

14:56.200 --> 14:57.680
I dare not call myself a wise ruler,

14:57.760 --> 14:59.200
but tonight,

14:59.280 --> 15:01.760
let all ministers drink to Dayin's peace.

15:01.840 --> 15:02.880
Join me in this cup.

15:04.760 --> 15:06.480
-Your Majesty is wise.
-Your Majesty is wise.

15:07.120 --> 15:09.240
Your Majesty is a sage ruler.

15:09.320 --> 15:13.400
Your Majesty is wise.
Your Majesty is a sage ruler.

15:14.960 --> 15:17.000
What a worthless emperor.

15:20.480 --> 15:22.920
Just as vile as his father.

15:44.760 --> 15:45.800
You're finally here.

15:45.880 --> 15:47.160
I've brought her.

15:48.000 --> 15:48.840
My lady,

15:48.920 --> 15:50.800
the osmanthus is in bloom.

15:51.320 --> 15:52.160
My lady,

15:52.680 --> 15:54.440
the osmanthus is in bloom.

15:54.960 --> 15:56.280
Bringing her here from the cold palace

15:56.360 --> 15:57.960
-wasn't easy.
-Fire…

15:58.520 --> 15:59.960
My lady, fire!

16:00.040 --> 16:02.040
-After that fire years ago,
-My lady…

16:02.120 --> 16:03.960
everyone in the palace
grew wary of this place.

16:04.480 --> 16:06.280
So hiding her here is safe enough.

16:06.360 --> 16:07.440
The osmanthus is in bloom…

16:07.520 --> 16:09.040
But she's completely

16:09.560 --> 16:11.560
disoriented, rambling, and incoherent.

16:12.160 --> 16:13.200
No clear memory at all.

16:13.280 --> 16:14.880
Fire!

16:14.960 --> 16:16.080
My lady.

16:16.160 --> 16:17.560
My lady.

16:20.240 --> 16:21.640
Commander Wei.

16:22.640 --> 16:24.040
Why are you back?

16:24.120 --> 16:25.360
My lady told you to run.

16:25.440 --> 16:26.640
Run.

16:26.720 --> 16:28.640
Run!

16:29.280 --> 16:30.360
Fire!

16:30.440 --> 16:31.560
Fire.

16:31.640 --> 16:32.480
Fire.

16:32.560 --> 16:34.040
Fire.

16:34.680 --> 16:36.000
Who is "my lady"?

16:37.920 --> 16:39.080
My lady.

16:39.640 --> 16:41.040
My lady is with child.

16:42.320 --> 16:43.720
Your Majesty, you can't strike her.

16:43.800 --> 16:45.560
Mother and child will both die!

16:49.040 --> 16:50.600
The osmanthus is in bloom.

16:50.680 --> 16:52.520
The osmanthus is in bloom.

16:54.600 --> 16:55.520
It's the Imperial Consort, Lady Qi.

16:56.160 --> 16:58.320
-So fragrant.
-This Qingyuan Palace

16:58.400 --> 17:00.200
was once her residence.

17:00.280 --> 17:01.760
Back then, she planted
many osmanthus trees here.

17:03.400 --> 17:04.599
Osmanthus.

17:04.680 --> 17:05.520
My lady.

17:06.040 --> 17:07.319
Osmanthus.

17:08.119 --> 17:09.079
My lady.

17:11.240 --> 17:12.680
I must make perfume with osmanthus.

17:15.880 --> 17:18.079
So fragrant. Who lit the incense?

17:18.680 --> 17:20.480
Who lit incense for my lady?

17:27.160 --> 17:29.120
It's a trap. Hold your breath!

17:29.960 --> 17:32.040
Marquis of Wu'an,

17:32.120 --> 17:36.200
you and that palace maid have already
inhaled the incense of desire.

17:37.040 --> 17:38.440
You cannot escape

17:38.520 --> 17:41.880
the crime of defiling the palace.

17:42.400 --> 17:45.200
If you're wise, surrender now.

17:46.240 --> 17:47.880
If you obey,

17:47.960 --> 17:49.000
His Majesty

17:49.080 --> 17:52.960
will surely spare your life.

18:00.760 --> 18:02.520
Marquis of Wu'an,

18:02.600 --> 18:05.200
no matter how brave you are,

18:05.280 --> 18:10.280
you can't escape
a trap like this, can you?

18:17.120 --> 18:18.560
General Fan, help!

18:18.640 --> 18:20.560
Someone must have discovered
that Her Highness was hiding someone.

18:21.080 --> 18:22.840
She told me to stay near Qingyuan Palace.

18:22.920 --> 18:24.560
But not long after the Marquis went in,

18:24.640 --> 18:26.160
Eunuch Li surrounded
the place with his men.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.640
So I rushed here to tell you.

18:29.360 --> 18:30.680
I'm going to Qingyuan Palace.

18:30.760 --> 18:31.640
You go find Empress Dowager An.

18:31.720 --> 18:33.760
But Her Highness said
Empress Dowager absolutely cannot know.

18:34.880 --> 18:36.600
Something terrible is about to happen.

18:37.440 --> 18:38.680
Only Empress Dowager An can handle this.

18:38.760 --> 18:40.160
-Go, quickly.
-Yes.

18:53.080 --> 18:53.920
Quick. Go!

18:54.000 --> 18:55.440
All of you go!

19:21.240 --> 19:23.040
Didn't he take the poison?

19:23.880 --> 19:25.920
Why can he still fight like this?

20:33.680 --> 20:35.360
Yan Zheng.

20:36.120 --> 20:37.760
Yan Zheng. Get up.

20:49.920 --> 20:51.000
Yan Zheng.

20:51.920 --> 20:53.280
What's happening?

20:53.800 --> 20:54.800
Changyu.

21:00.280 --> 21:01.480
Why are you so hot?

21:10.480 --> 21:11.760
How did you hurt your hand?

21:12.560 --> 21:13.600
Changyu.

21:22.080 --> 21:23.600
This place is too dangerous.

21:37.400 --> 21:38.240
Come here.

21:56.560 --> 21:57.600
Quick.

21:57.680 --> 21:58.600
Seal the palace gates!

21:59.280 --> 22:00.640
An assassin has broken
into the imperial garden.

22:00.720 --> 22:01.560
Yes, sir.

22:15.560 --> 22:16.680
Your Majesty,

22:16.760 --> 22:18.000
I offer you a toast.

22:20.760 --> 22:21.880
Grand Tutor.

22:22.400 --> 22:23.320
Chancellor Wei.

22:26.320 --> 22:28.200
Ministers, all.

22:34.320 --> 22:36.720
Where are my Marquis of Wu'an
and Flower-Adorned General?

22:36.800 --> 22:37.840
Why are they both missing?

22:38.440 --> 22:39.560
Your Majesty, terrible news!

22:40.080 --> 22:40.920
Your Majesty.

22:41.520 --> 22:43.320
The Marquis of Wu'an, drunk and depraved,

22:43.400 --> 22:44.800
has seized a palace maid,

22:44.880 --> 22:46.200
intent on violating her.

22:46.720 --> 22:47.840
I tried to stop him,

22:47.920 --> 22:51.320
but… the Marquis struck me down
and threw me out.

22:51.400 --> 22:52.240
How dare you!

22:53.160 --> 22:54.320
Slandering a high minister of the court.

22:54.920 --> 22:56.280
Do you know the penalty for that?

22:57.360 --> 22:58.800
I saw it with my own eyes.

22:58.880 --> 23:00.320
I wouldn't dare slander him.

23:01.720 --> 23:02.920
Your Majesty,

23:03.000 --> 23:05.720
could there be some misunderstanding here?

23:06.480 --> 23:09.520
Better to see for yourself.

23:09.600 --> 23:10.600
The Grand Tutor is right.

23:13.840 --> 23:15.400
You dog of a servant.

23:15.480 --> 23:17.680
How dare you slander
my loyal minister and capable general.

23:18.320 --> 23:19.480
Ministers.

23:20.480 --> 23:21.520
I'm here.

23:21.600 --> 23:23.080
Let's go see for ourselves.

23:23.160 --> 23:24.280
Yes, Your Majesty.

23:38.000 --> 23:40.480
Chancellor Wei, won't you come with me?

24:16.120 --> 24:17.640
I have urgent matters
to report to His Majesty.

24:17.720 --> 24:19.400
Emergency. No one may stop me.

24:19.480 --> 24:21.080
Minister Li, the palace banquet has begun.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.320
Without a decree, no one may enter.

24:22.400 --> 24:23.640
Violators will be dealt with
according to palace regulations.

24:24.280 --> 24:25.520
We're only following orders.

24:25.600 --> 24:26.520
Please understand, Minister Li.

24:27.800 --> 24:29.720
This is the palace pass
His Majesty granted our Li family.

24:29.800 --> 24:30.960
I am also among those invited.

24:31.040 --> 24:32.120
Is this still not permitted?

24:33.200 --> 24:34.400
Search over there.

24:34.480 --> 24:35.720
Go!

24:37.080 --> 24:38.360
That way, that way, and that way.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.680
I want every inch examined.

24:39.760 --> 24:42.000
You useless bunch of incompetents.

24:42.080 --> 24:43.800
A whole troop of you,

24:43.880 --> 24:45.480
and you can't find him?

24:46.200 --> 24:47.520
Search carefully!

24:48.040 --> 24:50.400
Chief Eunuch Li, terrible news.
There's a fire over there.

24:54.560 --> 24:55.400
Damn.

24:55.480 --> 24:57.280
The hunter becomes the hunted.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.720
What are you standing there for?

25:00.800 --> 25:02.280
Don't you see the fire?

25:02.360 --> 25:05.160
The Marquis of Wu'an
is trying to destroy the evidence!

25:05.240 --> 25:07.440
-Go put it out. Go!
-Yes, sir.

25:13.280 --> 25:17.880
QINGYUAN PALACE

25:18.720 --> 25:19.800
This…

25:19.880 --> 25:22.000
How did such a big fire
start all of a sudden?

25:22.080 --> 25:23.600
Reporting to Your Majesty.
Some eunuchs heard

25:23.680 --> 25:25.360
a palace maid shouting about a lecher.

25:25.440 --> 25:27.480
When my men arrived, they saw only…

25:29.520 --> 25:30.440
Saw who?

25:31.560 --> 25:34.040
They saw the Marquis of Wu'an
fleeing the hall.

25:34.120 --> 25:35.680
He also injured someone.

25:35.760 --> 25:37.320
Chief Eunuch Li
has taken men to pursue him.

25:37.400 --> 25:38.480
Fleeing?

25:38.560 --> 25:40.160
How could you let him flee?

25:40.240 --> 25:41.440
Your Majesty.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.840
Xie Zheng not only defiled the harem,

25:44.920 --> 25:45.880
but also tried to destroy the evidence.

25:45.960 --> 25:47.120
He should be arrested immediately.

25:47.200 --> 25:49.720
If he resists, kill him without mercy.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.120
Your Majesty.

25:57.200 --> 25:58.120
Your Majesty.

25:58.200 --> 25:59.680
-Empress Dowager.
-Your Majesty.

25:59.760 --> 26:01.520
Shu is still inside!

26:01.600 --> 26:02.720
-Shu!
-Empress Dowager…

26:02.800 --> 26:03.840
Empress Dowager.

26:03.920 --> 26:05.160
-Shu.
-Empress Dowager.

26:05.680 --> 26:07.000
Why are you stopping me?

26:07.080 --> 26:08.040
Go save her!

26:08.120 --> 26:10.640
Save her, now!

26:10.720 --> 26:12.600
Is the Grand Princess still inside?

26:12.680 --> 26:14.720
What are you standing there for?
Go put out the fire!

26:14.800 --> 26:16.320
-Yes!
-Go now!

26:17.040 --> 26:18.680
-Empress Dowager!
-Shu!

26:18.760 --> 26:20.000
-Empress Dowager!
-Don't go!

26:20.080 --> 26:22.680
-The fire's too big. You can't go in!
-Why are you stopping me?

26:22.760 --> 26:25.040
Empress Dowager, please,
take care of yourself.

26:25.120 --> 26:26.480
Enough talk. I'm going in.

26:28.360 --> 26:30.400
Wait. Gongsun Yin.

26:30.480 --> 26:31.480
-You shut up.
-I…

26:32.120 --> 26:33.040
And you.

26:33.560 --> 26:35.120
You dare talk to me like that?

26:37.800 --> 26:38.960
‎QINGYUAN PALACE

26:49.400 --> 26:50.240
Your Majesty,

26:50.320 --> 26:51.880
with this incident,

26:51.960 --> 26:54.880
the morale of the Marquis of Wu'an's
Yanzhou army will surely be shaken.

26:54.960 --> 26:58.720
And that Flower-Adorned General
who left mid-banquet,

26:58.800 --> 27:01.280
we should deal with her Jizhou forces
sooner rather than later.

27:01.360 --> 27:03.720
Then, Grand Tutor Li, what do you propose?

27:04.400 --> 27:07.160
I request Your Majesty's permission
to handle this matter with full authority.

27:08.720 --> 27:09.960
Shu.

27:12.320 --> 27:13.920
Once that group of soldiers passes,

27:14.000 --> 27:15.520
we'll run into the corridor.

27:19.440 --> 27:20.440
Don't move until then.

27:25.560 --> 27:26.600
Changyu…

27:28.640 --> 27:30.080
I love you--

27:31.280 --> 27:32.200
Someone's coming.

27:45.520 --> 27:47.080
I really do love you.

27:47.160 --> 27:48.360
Are you done or not?

28:11.000 --> 28:11.880
Who's there?

28:15.000 --> 28:16.680
There he is. After him!

28:19.080 --> 28:20.000
Stop!

28:27.120 --> 28:28.480
What kind of time is this?

29:04.520 --> 29:05.560
Shu!

29:06.240 --> 29:07.160
Shu!

29:07.680 --> 29:09.240
Your Highness, the Grand Princess.

29:09.320 --> 29:10.240
Shu!

29:10.800 --> 29:12.000
Your Highness.

29:12.080 --> 29:13.240
-Shu!
-Your Highness!

29:14.640 --> 29:15.880
Look.

29:17.600 --> 29:19.560
Shu… Shu isn't breathing.

29:19.640 --> 29:22.280
She… She's not breathing. Shu.

29:22.360 --> 29:23.960
Quick. Summon the imperial physician.

29:24.040 --> 29:25.560
-Summon the imperial physician now!
-Yes.

29:28.920 --> 29:30.360
Shu!

29:30.440 --> 29:31.840
If the Grand Princess

29:31.920 --> 29:33.280
lives as a witness,

29:33.360 --> 29:35.440
Xie Zheng could still clear himself.

29:35.960 --> 29:37.280
Whoever set this fire,

29:37.360 --> 29:39.360
they're ruthless.

29:45.360 --> 29:46.240
She's still breathing.

29:46.320 --> 29:47.440
Still!

29:56.080 --> 29:58.600
Gongsun Yin! You're defiling
the Grand Princess's honor,

29:58.680 --> 30:00.400
denying her peace even in death.

30:01.720 --> 30:03.160
-What are you doing?
-Empress Dowager.

30:03.240 --> 30:04.320
Someone once taught me this method.

30:04.400 --> 30:05.760
It can save a life.

30:05.840 --> 30:08.040
Let me ask you.
What matters more now, reputation or life?

30:08.640 --> 30:09.720
You…

30:11.360 --> 30:13.200
Save her. Save her, quickly!

30:14.760 --> 30:15.760
This…

30:28.440 --> 30:29.280
Your Majesty.

30:30.160 --> 30:31.560
You… How dare you!

30:32.280 --> 30:33.400
What is the meaning of this?

30:34.000 --> 30:35.840
Publicly defiling
the Grand Princess's honor.

30:35.920 --> 30:37.200
Where is the dignity
of the royal house now?

30:37.280 --> 30:39.360
-Yes.
-Guards. Seize him!

30:40.600 --> 30:42.360
I'd like to see who dares!

30:44.120 --> 30:46.680
In the first half of my life,
I killed too many.

30:46.760 --> 30:48.360
In my old age,
I live a life of fasting and prayer

30:48.440 --> 30:50.120
just to save my only daughter.

30:51.480 --> 30:53.720
If even Shu's life can't be saved,

30:53.800 --> 30:56.520
I don't mind killing a few more.

30:58.280 --> 31:00.120
Commander of the Imperial Guard,
hear my command.

31:00.200 --> 31:01.520
-I'm here.
-Here!

31:01.600 --> 31:03.320
Guard every entrance and exit tightly.

31:03.400 --> 31:05.880
If a single word
of today's events leaks out,

31:05.960 --> 31:08.200
everyone here, every last one of you,

31:08.280 --> 31:10.280
will die!

31:10.360 --> 31:11.680
-Understood.
-Understood.

31:13.000 --> 31:14.280
Follow me.

31:14.360 --> 31:16.200
Everyone… Everyone
obeys the Empress Dowager.

31:16.800 --> 31:17.720
Obeys the Empress Dowager.

31:17.800 --> 31:18.920
You, Gongsun,

31:19.000 --> 31:21.120
I command you to save her.

31:21.200 --> 31:22.920
If you fail to save Shu,

31:23.000 --> 31:24.320
you will die too.

31:38.400 --> 31:39.320
Shu!

31:43.480 --> 31:44.680
-Shu.
-You're awake.

31:45.200 --> 31:46.640
Shu, you're awake!

31:48.600 --> 31:50.120
-Shu.
-Your Majesty.

31:50.680 --> 31:53.480
Although Gongsun Yin
saved the Grand Princess,

31:53.560 --> 31:56.120
that doesn't prove Xie Zheng's innocence.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.880
Whether they conspired

31:57.960 --> 32:01.640
must be determined through interrogation.

32:03.160 --> 32:04.120
It…

32:05.520 --> 32:07.160
The one who saved the Grand Princess

32:07.680 --> 32:09.040
was a physician
from the Imperial Medical Bureau.

32:09.720 --> 32:11.600
Someone named Gongsun was never here.

32:17.400 --> 32:18.280
What does Empress Dowager An think?

32:19.240 --> 32:20.360
Indeed.

32:20.440 --> 32:22.680
Let today's matter end here.

32:24.200 --> 32:25.120
Yes.

32:25.200 --> 32:26.320
End it here.

32:26.840 --> 32:28.560
Let today's matter end here.

32:31.920 --> 32:33.120
Shu.

33:28.920 --> 33:30.960
Your Majesty,
we haven't found the culprit's trail yet.

33:31.040 --> 33:32.160
We're expanding the search.

33:33.520 --> 33:35.200
Your Majesty, were you looking for me?

33:46.600 --> 33:47.440
You two…

33:50.720 --> 33:52.560
Why are the two of you together?

34:02.440 --> 34:04.560
Minister, why are your clothes wet?

34:05.160 --> 34:07.200
I, drunk, fell into the lotus pond.

34:08.400 --> 34:10.520
Fortunately, the Flower-Adorned General
rescued me.

34:13.360 --> 34:14.320
Guards.

34:14.920 --> 34:17.000
Bring the Marquis
a change of clean clothes

34:17.520 --> 34:19.639
-and prepare a bowl of ginger soup.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

34:19.719 --> 34:20.639
Marquis of Wu'an!

34:21.159 --> 34:23.440
Tonight, Qingyuan Palace caught fire.

34:23.520 --> 34:25.360
The Grand Princess nearly lost her life.

34:25.440 --> 34:26.800
Someone testified

34:26.880 --> 34:30.159
that all of this was because you seized
a palace maid and debauched the harem,

34:30.239 --> 34:31.719
then tried to destroy the evidence.

34:32.239 --> 34:34.000
What do you have to say for yourself?

34:34.960 --> 34:37.320
I beg Your Majesty
to investigate thoroughly.

34:37.840 --> 34:40.080
The Marquis of Wu'an is the culprit.

34:41.000 --> 34:42.480
-You--
-I'm the culprit?

34:43.199 --> 34:46.040
Aren't your Imperial Guards
chasing the culprit?

34:46.760 --> 34:49.120
What? Is there a second culprit?

34:52.000 --> 34:53.760
Your Majesty. The culprit has been caught.

34:57.440 --> 34:59.160
-Bring him in.
-Yes.

35:19.240 --> 35:20.280
Your Li family,

35:20.960 --> 35:24.320
what a fine performance
of "righteousness over kin".

35:26.800 --> 35:28.080
How could it be you?

35:28.680 --> 35:31.000
Today, I only wished to confess
my feelings to the Grand Princess.

35:32.160 --> 35:33.760
I never expected such a misunderstanding.

35:35.480 --> 35:36.800
And to disturb Your Majesty as well.

35:37.800 --> 35:38.880
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

35:40.160 --> 35:41.000
This…

35:41.080 --> 35:42.480
I am the one who went to see
the Grand Princess.

35:43.600 --> 35:44.520
Not the Marquis of Wu'an.

35:45.160 --> 35:46.640
I beg Your Majesty to investigate.

35:52.520 --> 35:53.800
Why so many

35:53.880 --> 35:56.600
improprieties and misunderstandings
tonight?

35:58.040 --> 36:00.280
I share Your Majesty's curiosity.

36:00.800 --> 36:02.680
I've had a good capacity of alcohol.

36:03.800 --> 36:04.760
I wonder why

36:05.360 --> 36:07.760
one cup has me drunk tonight.

36:08.400 --> 36:12.040
Could it be that the fine wine
you bestowed was too potent?

36:14.360 --> 36:17.800
Those wines were aged
in the palace cellars for a long time.

36:18.520 --> 36:20.280
Naturally, they'd be a bit strong.

36:23.840 --> 36:25.320
The wine was all prepared

36:25.400 --> 36:27.440
by that servant Li Xiang himself,

36:27.520 --> 36:28.560
wasn't it?

36:28.640 --> 36:30.320
Could it be that you had other intentions?

36:35.080 --> 36:35.920
This…

36:38.240 --> 36:39.280
Your Majesty…

36:47.760 --> 36:48.880
Yes!

36:49.760 --> 36:50.920
This matter…

36:53.280 --> 36:58.040
I bear full responsibility.

36:59.640 --> 37:00.680
Only because

37:00.760 --> 37:04.240
the Marquis of Wu'an
humiliated me many times before.

37:05.400 --> 37:08.880
He even cut off one of my ears.

37:08.960 --> 37:09.800
So…

37:10.320 --> 37:13.040
So I harbored resentment all along.

37:13.120 --> 37:15.200
I wanted to use this chance…

37:16.080 --> 37:20.080
to frame him.

37:20.600 --> 37:22.520
-You--
-The fire in the Grand Princess's hall,

37:24.600 --> 37:25.760
you set that too?

37:27.680 --> 37:28.520
Enough!

37:28.600 --> 37:30.440
A base slave betrays his master.

37:30.520 --> 37:34.200
Your Majesty was deceived
by this servant too.

37:37.960 --> 37:39.360
Your Majesty.

37:39.440 --> 37:41.280
Tonight, someone clearly set a trap

37:41.360 --> 37:43.120
to frame me and the Marquis of Wu'an.

37:44.800 --> 37:46.200
I'm just a pig-slaughtering woman.

37:46.280 --> 37:47.560
I don't understand grand principles.

37:47.640 --> 37:49.400
But I've fought the enemy at the border,

37:49.480 --> 37:51.240
survived countless battles.

37:51.320 --> 37:52.200
And now, back home,

37:52.280 --> 37:54.240
I'm framed by my own people.

37:54.320 --> 37:55.760
I beg Your Majesty,

37:56.480 --> 37:57.440
Grand Tutor,

37:59.280 --> 38:00.280
or Chancellor Wei,

38:01.600 --> 38:03.040
to explain this to me.

38:05.200 --> 38:06.880
The state has its laws.

38:07.400 --> 38:10.400
Li Xiang is guilty.
Let the law handle him.

38:10.480 --> 38:13.000
This matter has nothing to do
with anyone else.

38:15.600 --> 38:16.920
Your Majesty,

38:17.000 --> 38:19.600
may I ask if the Dragon Spring Sword
you bestowed upon me

38:19.680 --> 38:20.840
still holds true?

38:32.200 --> 38:33.480
Of course it holds true.

38:45.960 --> 38:47.000
You…

38:48.800 --> 38:50.800
Your Majesty bestowed
the Dragon Spring Sword upon me.

38:50.880 --> 38:54.000
Then I cleared Your Majesty's
surroundings of traitors.

38:55.120 --> 38:56.280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

39:06.800 --> 39:08.040
All of you

39:08.640 --> 39:10.160
are my most vital ministers.

39:10.920 --> 39:14.080
Each has rendered great service to Dayin.

39:15.000 --> 39:16.480
Tonight's matter,

39:16.560 --> 39:18.400
I will investigate thoroughly.

39:18.480 --> 39:19.880
I will find the instigator

39:19.960 --> 39:21.080
and punish them without mercy.

39:24.520 --> 39:26.040
It's late.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.880
You may all return now.

39:33.360 --> 39:34.360
Let's go.

39:48.040 --> 39:48.880
Grandfather.

39:59.120 --> 40:00.000
Li Xiang.

40:09.840 --> 40:10.720
Chancellor Wei,

40:11.240 --> 40:12.480
why haven't you gone home yet?

40:12.560 --> 40:15.400
GUARD YOUR WORDS

40:15.480 --> 40:17.320
Seventeen years ago,

40:17.840 --> 40:19.960
the late emperor did the very same thing.

40:23.600 --> 40:24.840
You Qis

40:26.080 --> 40:28.200
really are of the same family.

40:32.760 --> 40:33.920
You…

40:34.960 --> 40:36.680
One last time.

40:46.000 --> 40:47.000
If it were the late emperor standing here,

40:47.840 --> 40:49.360
would the Chancellor
dare speak to him like this?

40:53.280 --> 40:54.680
Otherwise, how did your Majesty

40:55.520 --> 40:57.680
ascend the throne?

41:32.400 --> 41:34.520
-Everyone, take a look.
-Come and have a look!

41:34.600 --> 41:35.800
Take a look.

41:42.520 --> 41:43.720
Such a long gash.

41:45.400 --> 41:46.840
Shouldn't you go to the clinic?

41:57.600 --> 41:58.560
What are you doing?

42:19.360 --> 42:20.480
Calm down.

45:18.760 --> 45:22.400
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:22.480 --> 45:23.360
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
